OL,5, Millions of pounds have been paid out  
OL,6, in the last ten years to people who    
OL,7, were abused in the Scouts, lawyers say.
OL,9,FBBC File on 4 contacted 13 law firms   
OL,10,Fwho specialise in child abuse claims,  
OL,11,Fand data from the eight that responded 
OL,12,Frevealed more than #6m had been paid   
OL,13,Fout in compensation in the last decade.
OL,15,FSome 166 cases were settled over the   
OL,16,Fsame time, while more female survivors 
OL,17,Fwere now coming forward, lawyers said. 
OL,19,FThe Scout Association said it was      
OL,20,F"deeply sorry" anyone suffered abuse.  
